'''無邊際池'''（{{lang-en|infinity pool}}），是經過特殊設計，在視覺上似乎沒有邊界的[[水池|水池]]或[[游泳池|游泳池]]。無邊際池經過設計，有水流過其一個或多個邊界，在視覺上會有池子沒有邊界一直往外延伸的[[錯覺|錯覺]]。使池子看起和附近更大的水體例如海洋融成一體，或是其邊界就是天際線融合。這類池子常出現在富異國情調的[[渡假村|渡假村]]、五星級[[酒店|酒店]]、獨特的[[莊園|莊園]]、[[豪華住宅|豪華住宅]]、[[奢華|奢華]]的場所，或是廣告效果中<ref>{{cite news |last=Hiller |first=Jennifer |url=http://www.expressnews.com/lifestyle/home-garden/article/Ready-to-take-the-pool-plunge-6160832.php |title=Ready to take the pool plunge? |work=San Antonio Express-News |date=2015-03-27 |accessdate=2015-05-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305142231/http://www.expressnews.com/lifestyle/home-garden/article/Ready-to-take-the-pool-plunge-6160832.php|archivedate=2016-03-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Neal J. |last=Leitereg |url=http://www.latimes.com/business/realestate/hot-property/la-fi-hotprop-chris-bosh-mansion-20150326-story.html |title=Chris Bosh drops price on hilltop estate in Pacific Palisades |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=1965-03-07 |accessdate=2015-05-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307033602/http://www.latimes.com/business/realestate/hot-property/la-fi-hotprop-chris-bosh-mansion-20150326-story.html|archivedate=2016-03-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Osborne |first=Claudia |url=http://travelingsage.com/14-enchanting-infinity-pools/ |title=14 Enchanting Infinity Pools That Are Built to Take Your Breath Away |publisher=Traveling Sage |date=2015-03-04 |accessdate=2015-05-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518092440/http://travelingsage.com/14-enchanting-infinity-pools/ |archivedate=2015-05-18}}</ref>。

